{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"688","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"首波綠電轉供出爐 台積電等5家買逾億度綠電","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>工商時報 數位編輯<span lang='EN-US'> 2020.05.06</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/TSMC.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 405px;' />&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>圖<span lang='EN-US'>/</span>本報資料照片</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>《電業法》通過逾<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>年後，經濟部標準檢驗局今天宣布，正式完成國內第一波綠電轉供案例，此案總共涵蓋<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>家綠電生產商、<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>家綠電買主、<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>家綠電售電業，合計台積電、正崴精密共買賣一年<span lang='EN-US'>1.1</span>億度綠電。該局表示，後續還有多個轉供案在洽談中，預計會再多數個億度綠電交易。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>在《電業法》與《再生能源發展條例》相繼修正完成後，經濟部標準檢驗局一直積極推動國內綠電自由交易，也就是再生能源直、轉供。過去再生能源憑證僅是少量釋出供企業認購宣揚使用綠電，並非廠商跟企業直接買賣綠電。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>標檢局經媒合後，今日終於宣布完成國內第一批再生能源轉供案業者，其中有<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>家需要綠電企業，包含台積電、正崴精密、元太科技、大江生醫、正信不動產。<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>家綠電生產商，有台灣艾貴能源、曄恆能源、富崴能源、得禾能源、鴻元工程。<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>家綠電批發商，包含南方電力、瓦特先生及富威電力。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>這個交易囊括<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>個太陽光電廠的總裝置容量近<span lang='EN-US'>90.4MW</span>，可供應綠電超過<span lang='EN-US'>1.1</span>億度以上。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>標檢局指出，預估年度綠電總交易量需求業者涵蓋半導體業、電子零組件業、生技醫療業以及不動產業等。目前還有數項轉供案正在輔導中，可預期將有更多個億度綠電完成。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>(</span><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>中時 王玉樹<span lang='EN-US'>)</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: https://ctee.com.tw/news/policy/263845.html</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-05-06","clk_count":"102"}},"__N_SSG":true}